        <tr>
          <td class="post-content">
            <div class="post-content-inner">
              
              Well, I guess the first question is, &quot;Do you want to be an engineer?&quot; Obviously if you want to get a PE license at some point, then this isn't the school for you. But I think lots of other places that hire &quot;engineers&quot;, even without the PE license requirement, would balk at the non-ABET accreditation.<br /><br />On the other hand, if you're looking to work in some sort of field where you're not expected to be an engineer, but maybe more of a robotics/electronics guru, it might be reasonable to stay in that program.<br /><br />What sort of places are you thinking about working?

              

              
              
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
        
    </table>
    
