          <td class="post-content">
            <div class="post-content-inner">
              
              On looking at the website for that program, I'm kind of horrified that it's so hard to find the accreditation information. I mean, I know that the guy told you that the program isn't accredited, but I was wondering which of their engineering programs *are* - and I couldn't even find that. Best I could do was one blurb next to the list of undergrad engineering programs (of which there are 10 or more) saying that they have 9 accredited programs. What a crappy way of disseminating information.

              

              
              
            </div>
